                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330103-135-victim1347 t18330103-135-viclabel776"></join> to Mr. Bush, of St. Mildred's-court. On the 10th of December I was in <placeName id="t18330103-135-crimeloc777">Bridge-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18330103-135-crimeloc777" type="placeName" value="Bridge-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18330103-135-crimeloc777" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330103-135-off774 t18330103-135-crimeloc777"></join>, between six and seven o'clock in the evening; I felt a pull at my pocket - I turned round, and saw the prisoner close to me; I followed him over Blackfrairs-bridge without intimating that I suspected him - he attempted to turn down a street, and I stopped him; he was taken to the station, and my handkerchief was found concealed in the bottom of his trousers.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18330103-135-person1349">
