            . I am an officer. The prosecutor gave the prisoner into my charge - I found the handkerchief inside the lining at the bottom of his trousers; I searched him twice before I found it.</p>
               <p>Property produced and sworn to.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was out of employ.</p>
